ManagedBass does not need to be licensed for Commercial use, but bass and many of the addons have to be.

EntityPropertyConverter class provides functionality to flatten complex objects into dictionary of
	EntityProperties and functionality to recompose original object from the flattenned property dictionary.

	After the complex object is flattenned, it can be written into Azure Table Storage as DynamicTableEntity or
	serialized between web services including all of its original basic and nested complex properties.

	After retrieving the flat dictionary, ConvertBack method will recompose the original complex object.
